transcript: Help! My wife is unconscious and not breathing. She collapsed suddenly. Address is 123 Main St, Downtown. Please send an ambulance immediately!
There's a fire at my house! Smoke is everywhere, flames coming from the kitchen. Address is 456 Oak Ave, Suburbia. Need firefighters now!
Someone is breaking into my house! I hear glass breaking and footsteps. Address is 789 Pine Rd, Residential Area. Gunshots fired. Police needed immediately!
Car accident on Highway 101 near Exit 15. Multiple cars involved, people injured. Blood everywhere. Need ambulances and police.
Tornado warning! Severe weather approaching downtown. Taking shelter in basement. Large debris flying. Need emergency management.
My child has a high fever and is having trouble breathing. Not sure what to do. 555 Family Lane, Suburban Heights.
Small fire in my garage, mostly contained. Smoke alarm triggered. 777 Workshop Blvd, Industrial Park.
Neighbor's dog is loose and acting aggressively. Bit someone earlier. 222 Pet Street, Residential Zone.
Fender-bender on Main Street. Both drivers are ok, just car damage. Intersection of Main and First.
Power outage affecting several blocks. Trees down on power lines. Downtown electrical grid affected.
